V0101_01_00_00_0.text:
All right!
Get your game on!

V0101_01_00_01_0.text:
Time to throw down!
Win or lose, let's have fun!

V0101_01_00_02_0.text: Chazz, a Duel isn't about winning or losing. It's about having a sweet time!

V0101_01_00_03_0.text: Hey, I feel like we haven't thrown down in ages.

V0101_01_00_03_1.text:
Let's fix that. 
Time to Duel, Alexis!

V0101_01_00_04_0.text:
Hey Aster!
Our HEROES are going head to head? That's so chill!

V0101_01_00_05_0.text: You built a special Deck just to take me down? Sweet!

V0101_01_00_05_1.text: Maybe if you beat me, you'll be the school's #1 Duelist instead of me!

V0101_01_00_06_0.text:
Zane, you're not acting like yourself.
I'm gonna snap you out of it!

V0101_01_00_07_1.text: You're a nice guy, but I'm not gonna go easy on ya! That's not how I roll!

V0101_01_00_08_0.text:
Remember when we dueled during the entrance exam, Teach? 
And I won?

V0101_01_00_09_1.text: It's my fault that you've turned out like this...

V0101_01_00_10_0.text:
I get to duel Yugi? 
I must be dreaming!

V0101_01_00_11_0.text:
Just because you're my best bud doesn't mean I'll let you off the hook!
Let's do this, Sy!

V0101_04_00_02_0.text:
All I need is a chance...
I draw!

V0101_05_00_00_0.text: You're about to witness a miracle!

V0101_06_01_00_0.text: Sweet! Just what I was waiting for!

V0101_06_01_02_0.text: You gotta do better than that!

V0101_06_01_03_0.text: I won't let you do that!

V0101_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Polymerization!

V0101_08_00_01_0.text: Whenever there's trouble, a hero's one call away to save the day!

V0101_08_00_01_1.text:
My Trap Card activates!
Hero Signal!

V0101_08_00_02_0.text: My heroes love fighting in the big city!

V0101_08_00_03_0.text:
My Trap Card activates!
A Hero Emerges!

V0101_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Hero Barrier!

V0101_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
De-Fusion!

V0101_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
H - Heated Heart!

V0101_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
E - Emergency Call!

V0101_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
R - Righteous Justice!

V0101_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
O - Oversoul!

V0101_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Fusion Recovery!

V0101_08_00_12_0.text: I activate my Quick-Play Spell, The Flute of Summoning Kuriboh!

V0101_08_00_13_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Miracle Fusion!

V0101_08_00_13_1.text: It fuses Elemental HEROES that are in my Graveyard!

V0101_08_00_14_0.text: This is the perfect card for this moment!

V0101_08_00_14_1.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Sabatiel - The Philosopher's Stone!

V0101_08_00_15_0.text:
Here I come!
I activate the Field Spell, Neo Space!

V0101_08_00_16_0.text:
My Quick-Play Spell activates!
Flash Fusion!

V0101_08_00_17_0.text:
Hey, Chumley!
I'm playing the card you designed!

V0101_08_00_17_1.text: I activate the Field Spell, Skyscraper 2 - Hero City!

V0101_08_00_18_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Fifth Hope!

V0101_08_00_19_0.text:
Check out this Spell Card!
Reverse of Neos!

V0101_08_00_20_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Contact Out!

V0101_08_00_21_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Instant Neo Space!

V0101_08_00_22_0.text:
My Trap activates!
Terra Firma Gravity!

V0101_08_00_22_1.text: Terra Firma's gravitational forces pull Level 4 or lower monsters toward him!

V0101_08_00_23_0.text: I owe it to my friends to overcome my fear and use this card for good.

V0101_08_00_23_1.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Super Polymerization!

V0101_08_00_24_0.text: Here's the power that protects all of Neo Space!

V0101_08_00_24_1.text: I activate the Spell Card, Wrath of Neos!

V0101_08_00_25_0.text:
Winged Kuriboh!
Show 'em you're tough as you are cute!

V0101_08_00_26_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Mask Change!

V0101_08_00_27_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Mask Change II!

V0101_08_00_28_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Miracle Contact!

V0101_08_00_29_0.text:
I activate my trap!
Final Fusion!

V0101_08_00_29_1.text: We take damage equal to the combined ATK of our monsters!

V0101_08_00_31_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Instant Fusion!

V0101_08_00_32_0.text: Come on back from another dimension!

V0101_08_00_32_1.text: I activate the Spell Card, Parallel World Fusion!

V0101_08_00_33_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Skydive Scorcher!

V0101_08_00_34_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Form Change!

V0101_08_00_35_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
A Hero Lives!

V0101_08_00_36_1.text: I discard two cards to activate Transcendent Wings!

V0101_09_00_00_1.text: You take damage equal to the destroyed monster's ATK!

V0101_09_00_04_1.text:
Winged Kuriboh!
Send back all their energy!

V0101_09_00_06_0.text: I'll use Necroshade's effect from the Graveyard!

V0101_09_00_09_1.text: I Special Summon two Fluff Tokens in Defense Position!

V0101_10_00_00_0.text: Here comes one of my favorites!

V0101_10_00_02_0.text: I know you'll help me out!

V0101_11_00_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0101_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0101_13_00_00_0.text: Soar on in, Elemental HERO Avian!

V0101_13_00_01_0.text:
I'll summon this!
Elemental HERO Burstinatrix!

V0101_13_00_03_0.text:
It's everyone's favorite golden boy!
Elemental HERO Sparkman!

V0101_13_00_04_0.text:
Here comes the hero to both you and me!
Elemental HERO Flame Wingman!

V0101_13_00_05_0.text: Say hello to Elemental HERO Thunder Giant!

V0101_13_00_06_0.text: I know I can always count on you, Winged Kuriboh!

V0101_13_00_07_0.text: Show 'em how you've evolved, Winged Kuriboh LV9!

V0101_13_00_08_0.text: Winged Kuriboh evolves all the way to LV10!

V0101_13_00_10_0.text: Give a big welcome to Elemental HERO Bladedge!

V0101_13_00_14_0.text:
It's your time to shine!
Elemental HERO Shining Flare Wingman!

V0101_13_00_15_0.text: I'm callin' up Elemental HERO Electrum!

V0101_13_00_18_0.text: Neo Space has a brand new hero!

V0101_13_00_18_1.text: And his name is Elemental HERO Neos!

V0101_13_00_19_0.text: Swim in, Elemental HERO Aqua Neos!

V0101_13_00_21_0.text: Join the party, Neo-Spacian Flare Scarab!

V0101_13_00_22_0.text: Dig me up a victory, Neo-Spacian Grand Mole!

V0101_13_00_23_0.text:
Get a load 'a this bad boy!
Neo-Spacian Glow Moss!

V0101_13_00_25_0.text: Here's the one and only Elemental HERO Marine Neos!

V0101_13_00_27_0.text: Bring the chaos, Elemental HERO Chaos Neos!

V0101_13_00_28_0.text: From the depths of space, I call upon Elemental HERO Storm Neos!

V0101_13_00_34_0.text: Come on down, Elemental HERO Honest Neos!

V0101_13_00_36_0.text: Take to the skies, Elemental HERO Stratos!

V0101_13_00_39_0.text: Elemental HERO Neos Knight takes the field!

V0101_13_00_41_0.text:
Fuse and transform!
Contrast HERO Chaos!

V0101_13_00_46_0.text: This HERO is sure to send chills down your spine!

V0101_13_00_48_0.text: Come on out, Elemental HERO Core!

V0101_13_00_50_0.text: I'm firing up Elemental HERO Blazeman!

V0101_13_00_51_0.text: Say hi to my trusty Elemental HERO Woodsman!

V0101_13_00_52_0.text: From the deep, here comes Elemental HERO Ocean!

V0101_16_00_01_0.text: The hero always wins in the end!

V0101_19_00_02_0.text: Meet Clayman, up close and personal!

V0101_19_00_04_0.text: Turn up the heat, Flame Wingman!

V0101_19_00_14_0.text: Light em up, Shining Flare Wingman!

V0101_19_00_18_1.text:
Unleash your power and defend Neo Space!
Cosmic Crush!

V0101_21_00_00_0.text:
I end my turn!
Your move!

V0101_21_00_02_0.text: Argh... All I can do is end my turn.

V0101_28_00_00_0.text:
Oh yeah!
There's nothing better than a Duel!

V0101_28_00_00_1.text: Until next time, keep gettin' your game on!

V0101_28_00_01_0.text:
Sweet!
You gave me quite a challenge!

V0101_28_00_01_1.text: You might just be the second best Duelist here!

V0101_28_00_02_0.text: I may have won, but you definitely got game!

V0101_28_00_02_1.text: Can't wait to Duel you again!

V0101_28_00_03_1.text:
That was fun! 
The trash talking, the action... It's all great!

V0101_28_00_04_0.text:
And that's game!
That was one sweet Duel!

V0101_28_00_04_1.text: Never a boring moment with you, Alexis!

V0101_28_00_05_0.text: There's a hero in each of us.

V0101_28_00_05_1.text: And you always gotta give the hero a time to shine!

V0101_28_00_06_0.text:
You never stop giving me a challenge, Bastion!
I can't wait to see what you come up with next!

V0101_28_00_07_0.text:
Zane, you're already a legend at Duel Academy.
But I'll be a bigger legend someday. That's a promise!

V0101_28_00_08_1.text: Your Crystal Beasts are super sweet!

V0101_28_00_09_1.text: I passed the test again, Teach!

V0101_28_00_10_0.text: You're not gonna be alone anymore, Yubel.

V0101_28_00_10_1.text: I'll help you find the right path again.

V0101_28_00_12_1.text:
That was a sweet Duel!
I'm on the road to becoming the next King of Games!

V0101_28_00_13_0.text: You gotta get your game on, Sy.

V0101_28_00_13_1.text: Or else, you'll never beat Zane.

V0101_29_00_01_1.text:
I may flunk now and then, but I never fail in the end.
Let's Duel again sometime!

V0101_29_00_02_1.text:
But I won't next time!
Thanks for the sweet Duel!

V0101_29_00_04_0.text: Just when I think I'm gonna win, you always have another combo ready!

V0101_29_00_05_0.text: You always have the sweet moves, Aster!

V0101_29_00_06_0.text:
Tight Duel, Bastion!
Man, I can't wait to see what Deck you'll bring next time!

V0101_29_00_07_0.text: Zane, I guess I still have a lot to learn to reach your level.

V0101_29_00_08_0.text:
Hmm...
Maybe I shoulda played that other card last turn.

V0101_29_00_09_0.text: You really know your stuff, Teach!

V0101_29_00_09_1.text: I guess I won't be teaching you a lesson until next time!

V0101_29_00_10_1.text: Is there really nothing I can do to change your mind?

V0101_29_00_11_0.text: The people are right. You really are tough!

V0101_29_00_11_1.text: No wonder you're the King of Games!

V0101_29_00_12_0.text: Looks like you've improved your game again, Sy!

V0101_30_00_00_0.text:
What's up?
Show me your next move!

V0101_30_00_01_0.text: C'mon, you don't need to be scared of my HEROES.

V0101_30_00_02_0.text:
Don't give up yet!
Because getting out of a jam will feel sweet!

V0101_33_00_01_0.text: Time to get my game on!

V0101_33_00_02_0.text: I'll show you my HERO's power!

V0101_34_00_01_0.text:
Don't underestimate me because I'm in Slifer Red.
Or else, you'll be seeing stars!

V0101_34_00_02_0.text: My Elemental HERO is super sweet!

V0101_34_00_04_0.text:
You might just be the second best Duelist here!
Because I'm #1!

V0101_34_00_06_0.text:
Whoa!
You can see monster spirits too?

V0101_34_00_08_0.text: HEROES are awesome, almost as awesome as Dueling!

V0101_35_00_00_0.text: Wanna Duel? Let's get our game on!

V0101_35_00_01_0.text: My Heroes are ready to throw down!

V0101_27_00_00_0.text: Argh... I let my guard down!

V0101_01_00_12_0.text: You're the darkness that's inside my heart?

V0101_28_00_14_0.text:
Get out of here!
I won't let the darkness control me!
